<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Bloom‘s Taxonomy Verbs</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">前人已经总结了很多Bloom‘s Taxonomy的动词词库</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200909/2b06e74d784b4ba58e15b15ba1f31c4a.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">source: https://tips.uark.edu/using-blooms-taxonomy/</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有一个版本也很不错，可以作为相互补充</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200909/9ee8896f573942f2a5a8ce91584f632a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>如何在文书中应用bloom‘s taxonomy？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选取了两个PS中的句子，让大家感受一下这些Bloom‘s Taxonomy中涉及的动词是如何展现出你的学习结果或学习目标的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Taking part in the Young Enterprise Scheme in the role of financial director allowed me to showcase my numerical and logical skills. I was able to <strong>present</strong> the accounts of the company and dictate where the costs were allocated. [present, apply类动词]</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">I am fascinated by child language acquisition as this is something so different to what I have studied previously. Through guided reading and supporting younger students I have been able to observe different aged children and <strong>assess</strong> their reading abilities and the way in which they use language. [assess， evaluate 类动词]</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">当然，Bloom‘s Taxonomy不是万能的，需要你在有确切的已经发生的学习事实时，才能事半功倍。所以先准备好素材，才能让自己的PS写作更为顺畅！</p>